    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the endless world of Steinstern. Explore increasingly large procedural mazes and unlock the doors. Find and upgrade weapons and level-up your ship to stand a chance against the increasingly difficult enemies.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect EXP to upgrade your ship with randomized level-ups.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find weapons in different rarities (used &lt; normal &lt; good &lt; rare &lt; epic &lt; legendary) with special attributes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy, sell or upgrade weapons at the  workshop.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Offers a wide range of difficulties from 'very easy' to 'very hard'</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Both keyboard  and mouse or gamepad will work equally well.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playable in locale coop with dynamic split-screen with two controllers [🎮🎮] on the same PC .</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is no artifical cap on player, enemy, or weapon levels.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find a way through quadrangular and hexangular mazes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538030/extras/edc4dc9b3b2430b835fb6d67905bf535.avif?t=1771968095\" width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock the doors by guessing the right combination:  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538030/extras/18d3e74112f3f1e67c7c0f134aaa2384.poster.avif?t=1771968095\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538030/extras/18d3e74112f3f1e67c7c0f134aaa2384.webm?t=1771968095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538030/extras/18d3e74112f3f1e67c7c0f134aaa2384.mp4?t=1771968095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538030/extras/fdfd81d87864877f355367f445c6a097.poster.avif?t=1771968095\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538030/extras/fdfd81d87864877f355367f445c6a097.webm?t=1771968095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538030/extras/fdfd81d87864877f355367f445c6a097.mp4?t=1771968095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ... or by throwing the ball in the basket:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538030/extras/15f1375f17c379c2a7b74d21a0b5e642.poster.avif?t=1771968095\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538030/extras/15f1375f17c379c2a7b74d21a0b5e642.webm?t=1771968095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538030/extras/15f1375f17c379c2a7b74d21a0b5e642.mp4?t=1771968095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can buy, sell or upgrade weapons at the workshop:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538030/extras/e5d867c2f18a66d826dbbb1438e5d50c.avif?t=1771968095\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538030/extras_big/e5d867c2f18a66d826dbbb1438e5d50c.avif?t=1771968095 width=1560 height=738 /></span></p>",
